{"tid":834033,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實玫瑰好愛小王子","createTime":"2018-09-24T02:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T01:17:03.000Z","uid":84338,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9190d4e489bbcc760bb06bb1524e5525ad0067","tid":834033,"uid":84338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:36:37.000Z","msg":"只係玫瑰唔識得點去愛小王子<br />\n先會令到小王子離開左玫瑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4748b0f438325d3baf26638535153c7f18b4caad","tid":834033,"uid":84338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f311d6329391ca3ad25c9f4ba528836fa2503a","tid":834033,"uid":84338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65aa9f7f4def188f86605012370b34caaebbbcf","tid":834033,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"樓主仲喺唔喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺"},{"pid":"b15b1ffa34ba1d3e1b17c328cbfda041d0606835","tid":834033,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T21:34:13.000Z","msg":"[/quote]我明，<br />\n我真係明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係玫瑰屌走小王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過玫瑰愛佢㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係愛佢㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「我一向太傻了。請你原諒我，快活起來吧！」<br />\n<br />\n「不錯，我愛你。你一直都不曉得，那是我的過錯。這個沒有關係，但是你也和我一樣傻。快活起了吧﹒﹒﹒把這個玻璃罩拿開，我不再需要它了。」<br />\n<br />\n「不要這樣扭扭怩怩的，這樣很討厭。你既然決定要走就走吧！」<br />\n<br />\n玫瑰係真係愛佢㗎。。。[/quote]"},{"pid":"442e445456560ed6a4123bf2acaf887f70a4600d","tid":834033,"uid":84338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65aa9f7f4def188f86605012370b34caaebbbcf","tid":834033,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"樓主仲喺唔喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哇 十年前"},{"pid":"e9fce8d15c5ba34a5aa3d6ead739307b7e5b0626","tid":834033,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442e445456560ed6a4123bf2acaf887f70a4600d","tid":834033,"uid":84338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65aa9f7f4def188f86605012370b34caaebbbcf","tid":834033,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"樓主仲喺唔喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哇 十年前"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T05:09:08.000Z","msg":"半夜睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得要幫仆街玫瑰伸冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf38f02ea758a4f8db9fc40128cbd7361075aec","tid":834033,"uid":84338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fce8d15c5ba34a5aa3d6ead739307b7e5b0626","tid":834033,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442e445456560ed6a4123bf2acaf887f70a4600d","tid":834033,"uid":84338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65aa9f7f4def188f86605012370b34caaebbbcf","tid":834033,"uid":345195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"樓主仲喺唔喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"